    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/sannqi/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u54380617-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sannqi/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">容瑜</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-11-21"
      class="main-meta">2013-11-21 17:48:42</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6426256_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  刚刚看完书之国，非常好看，好羡慕日本浓厚的读书气氛，想起南京地铁站里的移动书屋有很多人去，周末去书店还是有很多人在里面买书读书就很开心，不过如果我们能更爱读书一点好了，地铁上鲜少见到有人捧着书看呢，基本上都是在玩手机……据调查，日本即便是繁忙的中小企业总经...

